latestIgtvVideos.title: TOP 3 Pinky NUDE LIPSTICKS💋💄
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So , instead of focusing on the COLOR of the lipstick 
I  took time to pick these out for you guys BASED ON THE FORMULA ! 

Firstly ,
@facescanada in Sweet Mocha💕
 
This falls on the creamy mattes side , it is moisturising and the color/pigmentation is totally Buildable ! 👏🏼
I ❤️ this shade for an everyday subtle flush of color 
-
@trysugar lip crayon in Elle Woods💕
 
This has a powdery matte feel but it doesn’t dry out your lips which I like . It comes in a pencil ✏️ form and the color Payoff is Insane ! 😻
-
@kyliecosmetics  Lip in Candy K 💕

This is a Complete Matte Liquid Lip , color payoff is good. 
But ,
I cannot use this alone  I always have to ! Have to line my lips first with a lip liner that’s atleast 3 shades Darker . as the color , alone , is too pale for me (medium to olive skin spectrum) 
And I Don’t mind doing this step , I quite enjoy it ☺️
I used the @wetnwildindia in Chestnut
And it looks Beaut 😻 and smells like coconut 🥥 🖤
The only thing I DO NOT like about not just this one , but any Liquid lipstick in general is they are very drying !! And they Crack!! No matter how much lip balm you put beneath it 🥺
.

Hope you guys liked how I did this

latestIgtvVideos.title: Nail Buffing 💅🏻 Cut File Polish Routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey loves 💓 
Made a video showing how I do my Nails , All at Home ! .
First off ,  I remove any left out nail paint with the @healthandglow nail remover . Then,I trim to get the shape I want and then smoothen it out by shaping it with a file
.
Use a cuticle oil to remove your cuticles , I’m using the one by @nisacosmetics peach cuticle oil
.
Then I Buff my nails with a nail buffer by @nisacosmetics •strengthens •promotes healthy growth and circulation of blood •gives you shiny nails .
Nail paint - I use my top coat polish as my base coat as well . Works for me . Lasts about a week long . I do a base coat , 2 layers of nail colour , and top coat . That’s like 4 layers of polish haha. .
Used the @reliancetrends top coat  @trysugar seal the slate .
And lastly , Hand Cream - moisturising after alll of this is super important, I used the @marksandspencerindia Honey suckle nail and hand cream . Smells divine! .
That’s it , hope ya like it ❤️ .

DIY HAIR OIL FULL RECIPE ⬇️

Herbs & seeds you’ll need🍃
Hibiscus flower (fresh or dried) (hair strength, reduces greying)
Kalonji seeds (hair growth, scalp health)
Henna leaves (reduces greying, hair fall control, natural conditioner)
2-3 small size onions (Hair fall)
Hibiscus leaves (Hair thickening, shine, hair growth)
Curry leaves Hair growth, hair fall control)
Methi/ Fenugreek seeds (improved texture, scalp health) 

Oils you’ll need🛢️
Coconut oil 1 litre 
Castor oil 250 ml
Almond oil few tbsp

Preparation:
Heat the coconut + castor oils in a big air dish for 5 mins on low flame. Turn off the flame and add in all the ingredients, mix it well.
Add almond oil. Let the oil set aside for 2 complete days. Strain after 2 days and store in an air tight bottle.
